eplyTime":"2018-09-01T23:42:17.000Z","msg":"爐石個位清唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:58:01.000Z","msg":"電競係亞運表演項目唔計入獎牌榜<br />\n<br />\n所以應該唔會有獎金"},{"pid":"476ad8eefbc730ce04984f9f1ae64119cb241ba5","tid":802833,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6047cfa5cac4041fffc2697ca57061b9a787d25","tid":802833,"uid":87571,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:28:47.000Z","msg":"香港全職運動員每個月有資助，金額視乎自己屬唔屬於係精英運動員。所以未至於完全貼錢貼時間玩。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報2016年有講過呢方面嘅資料<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;只有隸屬精英項目的健兒，才有資格向政府申請個人資助。至於一個運動員獲得多少資助金額，便要視乎其個人成績。按照表現，這些精英運動員會被編入個十級：最高為「精英甲+級」，像李慧詩便是一例，但她每月也不過拿到三萬多元；至於次一級的「精英甲級」，例如剛退役的陳振興和歐鎧淳，即使全職也不足二萬五千元；而一個非A級項目、非全職的「青少年隊」運動員，每月就只得$570訓練津貼。根據體院提供的資料，目前「A*級」項目有159位運動員獲得訓練津貼，而「A級」項目則有560位運動員。而每個「B級」項目，目前則有800多名運動員受不同程度的支援。至於非精英運動員，在現存機制下便幾乎拿不到任何資助和配套，甚至連出國比賽也要自己貼錢。 &ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20161015/55776845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20161015%2F55776845&d=5TLoamFMl8FqW3ZB8ORoLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=80ff1317\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20161015%2F55776845&h=6acd3fdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20161015/55776845</a><br />\n<br />\n今次攞金牌嘅欖球隊成員屬於精英所以每個月應該有兩三萬資助。有得玩自己鍾意嘅嘢有依個人工其實唔算太差。<br />\n<br />\n運動員資助名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hksi.org.hk/tc/recipient-list/recipient-list-of-elite-training-grant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksi.org.hk%2Ftc%2Frecipient-list%2Frecipient-list-of-elite-training-grant&d=5TLoamFMl8FqW3ZB8ORoLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1d1d36bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hksi.org.hk/tc/recipient-list/recipient-list-of-elite-training-grant</a>"},{"pid":"0952cf2cadd4d2df089e965e0eccc6687bc28a63","tid":802833,"uid":155079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"教下班二世祖，鬼佬打rugby都應該夠過一世"},{"pid":"35dc03d87d406240d634a463a0d6f737d4601ac8","tid":802833,"uid":56321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"「運動員這條路絕對有出路」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">除咗無家底又無人脈嘅泳隊隊員</span>"},{"pid":"c99cdc4250f226fd09077ab09046f53e6c479f4d","tid":802833,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0be23157f8a22a25c24bb8028fbe9fc82921ffc","tid":802833,"uid":87571,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"fef326ecd1a3c65d9487917b7800a85966c630aa","tid":802833,"uid":51129,"like":10,"dislike":64,"score":-54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:38:25.000Z","msg":"出路出路，個金牌值幾錢先？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:52:03.000Z","msg":"個人項目一個金牌有80萬<br />\n團隊項目一個金牌有160萬，不過要成組人分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hksi.org.hk/tc/support-to-athletes/awards/cash-incentives-for-hong-kong-medallists-at-18th-asian-games\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksi.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fsupport-to-athletes%2Fawards%2Fcash-incentives-for-hong-kong-medallists-at-18th-asian-games&d=5TLoamFMl8FqW3ZB8ORoLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c02e39d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hksi.org.hk/tc/support-to-athletes/awards/cash-incentives-for-hong-kong-medallists-at-18th-asian-games</a><br />\n<br />\n李慧詩2金1銀攞咗大約二百萬獎金"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:50:28.000Z","msg":"咁有d團隊項目多人d,有d少人d<br />\n要平均分既條數咪差好遠?"},{"pid":"4915f9e729f9334d7bfa9010627ed4a38b7b484d","tid":802833,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"397ad4c2d7f45901ae83fe982805d7fc42da9ccf","tid":802833,"uid":65530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:51:32.000Z","msg":"d鬼本身就係有錢仔，個個讀國際學校出身，根本唔洗擔心出路問題"},{"pid":"753f4574b789c950a986ac7f7c90f5a35fe2eabd","tid":802833,"uid":23141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"055ae6748ac7953aae9fa29ea3b7e20fe1012b6c","tid":802833,"uid":51129,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cdd5ad3b2e199ea29820459cfd72246581f28ee0","tid":802833,"uid":23141,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T19:24:03.000Z","msg":"點解你班契弟覺得出路一定要係名成利就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好簡單各施所長，有個decent 嘅生活咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n記者係鍾意揀bite 㗎啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:12:24.000Z","msg":"出路 =<br />\n1. 當你去到行業頂尖水平，可以名成利就大富大貴<br />\n2. 就算你天資有限，只係去到行業平凡嘅水平，都起碼可以有個decent嘅生活<br />\n<br />\n亞運金牌可以勉強維到生，呢的唔撚叫出路囉有冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:54:01.000Z","msg":"本身頂尖就係有大把人墊底㗎啦<br />\n跳咗呢個step,一嚟就想玩運動藝術科學呢班友名成利就根本無咩可能<br />\n唔做大個餅，等至少天資有限，未足以去到奧運獎牌之類水平可以有decent 生活，根本行業去水準好難提升，英超個個幾百萬一個月，咪成堆英甲英乙，但佢地係咪要乞食呢<br />\n<br />\n一堆人讀醫讀law 會計呢啲可以有出路，本身就係ce al dse 大學選科幫佢不斷箍人，佢地就係頂尖水平（考試上），一堆人轉咗去做sales、勞動階層、低薪文職勉強維生<br />\n宜家咪一大班人底層人買唔到樓，就算租樓都生活愈來愈差囉，根本大環境係咩人都無decent 生活，貧富懸殊，永遠只可以最top 舔哂所以嘢<br />\n<br />\n所以咁當然可以話一千幾日個項目幫得邊個<br />\n運動又要資助、藝術又要、電影又要、乜柒都要"},{"pid":"3bd0459dba31bc9f7e4f2b765a9176f2e812ab22","tid":802833,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"出路係拍廣告"},{"pid":"b50d3ccb5b835003df73b0059c9ad73058332fcb","tid":802833,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"場地單車 , 劍擊隊 ,  羽毛波 ,  保齡波,  風帆 可以重點發展下 <br />\n<br />